title: Final Fantasy IX Original Soundtrack [.MP3]
description:
Ughh, I screwed up uploading this the first time, sorry everyone D:
Hopefully I get it right this time.

K, once again, FF9 OST, I uploaded it as a .zip this time instead of just the folder or whatever, sorry if that&#039;s an inconvenience for anyone =/
(This is also the reason it&#039;s under the "other" category this time)

All files are .MP3 format.
Enjoy :)   (if I didn&#039;t screw up again lmfao)
